name: SkyDivers Survival
description:
Try to survive falling down with a broken parachute!

- Unlock all unique characters
- Avoid airplanes, bombs and even ducks
- Addictive gameplay
- Earn some money while falling
- Feel insane speed

You are falling from the airplane or helicopter or whatever. This is a free falling survival game!

Don't panic!
Choose your favourite pet or unicorn or sausage and fall down from skies!
I bet you will become a legend of sky diving!
